{"tid":1763272,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[砌女] 20~25k想砌條打機勁既女 求指教","createTime":"2019-11-30T08:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T15:09:32.000Z","uid":75767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7b802673bbee6a79747d97b2f19ce0b48c4cf92f","tid":1763272,"uid":75767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:10:29.000Z","msg":"小弟5年前砌既女 而家先有叫有錢再砌過條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/unwcAEd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FunwcAEd.png&h=9ac2abd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 請講低Budget<br />\n唔連moon 唔連sdd, hdd<br />\n大約20~25k 可以加多d既 都儲左一排錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 電腦主要用途<br />\n打機打機打機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n期待部新機可以玩到絕大部分既UHD mod.. 全部都係玩單機驚 一直都有入skyrim ,GTA5, witcher3 行下街望下風景 .. 下年既cyberpunk當然會玩<br />\n唔需要直播 / 錄製<br />\n<br />\n3. 個人需求<br />\n首先想講我垃圾眼分唔到高效同中效光追 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以光追需求唔大<br />\n目前部機只玩到中效 上面都講希望玩到ultra (主要玩mod) 最好當然希望大部分都60fps 但如果筆直有限行唔哂60既話 30我都無問題 鬼叫我窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對上update部機係5年前 而家有返工應該有能力2~3年update一次部機<br />\n唔駛超頻<br />\n想靜 而家部腦個fan都ok大聲 (D塵好難清)<br />\n比較prefer intel (但其實無用過amd, google過好多人話amd性價比較高 但inter比較for打機)<br />\nRGB就唔駛咁7彩 想要下圖呢種單紫色咁樣 (唔知行價 希望巴打可以堤供一下整到咁樣大約咩價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者下次有筆直再另外整)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VijYwcB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVijYwcB.png&h=a5d96d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F55HXSB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF55HXSB.png&h=e1ab999c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋間房多塵 而家個case唔大 d線堆埋哂一齊 好逼好難清塵 好似佢咁樣就會易D清塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 現在或將會使用mon的類型<br />\nmoon暫時唔駛買住 要等下年儲錢另外再買個靚moon, 到時應該另外預15~20k左右<br />\n4k, 240hz, 打機21:9夠了<br />\nprefer 流暢度 &gt; 畫質<br />\n<br />\n5. wishlist<br />\nCPU : i9 9900K<br />\nMB : pls advise<br />\nRAM : pls advise<br />\nDisplay card : 2080ti (覺得titan同2080ti好似唔差太遠, 但上網睇過1080ti, 2080ti又好似唔係差好遠 垃圾眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\nHDD, SSD : 已有<br />\nPSU , CASE, CPU COOLER : pls advise<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係大po留左言但暫時無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該哂各位巴打了"},{"pid":"484ef19c3356d8a74bc20806a9f84e7feb0e7f56","tid":1763272,"uid":21961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:13:34.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f20ebed8643e8f95f5a6bb181f9a668a833a8be","tid":1763272,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec86fd8152869735b3c6153deb91143f483605d0","tid":1763272,"uid":44718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:33:24.000Z","msg":"唔好買2080TI住, 聽聞2020年初會出2080TI SUPER<br />\n而且聽講可能會用返原粒TU102<br />\n真係有錢又唔係緊急換機嘅我建議睇多排先, 等佢跌價又好, 買新卡又好"},{"pid":"bbc41b6e6812c0e4a1023abaaa88df806ce365b6","tid":1763272,"uid":28668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:35:09.000Z","msg":"2萬幾點都唔算窮砌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求其執信仰list"},{"pid":"946e41b81c2dee70e094728ad031bcdaa566ea83","tid":1763272,"uid":75767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbc41b6e6812c0e4a1023abaaa88df806ce365b6","tid":1763272,"uid":28668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:35:09.000Z","msg":"2萬幾點都唔算窮砌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求其執信仰list"},"citedBy":0,